So if you truly
change your mind,

00:24:22.140 --> 00:24:24.120 align:middle line:84%
there should be
evidence in your life.

00:24:24.120 --> 00:24:26.590 align:middle line:84%
So most people,
as I said earlier,

00:24:26.590 --> 00:24:28.680 align:middle line:84%
