00:24:28.680 --> 00:24:30.400 align:middle line:90%
in their personal reality.

00:24:30.400 --> 00:24:32.160 align:middle line:84%
But they're still
the same personality.

00:24:32.160 --> 00:24:33.810 align:middle line:90%
We have to become somebody else.

00:24:33.810 --> 00:24:36.480 align:middle line:84%
So if you were to
sit down and you

00:24:36.480 --> 00:24:39.450 align:middle line:84%
