a new way of being,

00:24:39.450 --> 00:24:43.290 align:middle line:84%
a new thought that would connect
to a new emotion, that could

00:24:43.290 --> 00:24:46.260 align:middle line:84%
drive you to plan
a new behavior,

00:24:46.260 --> 00:24:48.510 align:middle line:84%
and you reviewed
that enough times,

00:24:48.510 --> 00:24:51.900 align:middle line:84%
there's a good possibility that
you would change your brain

00:24:51.900 --> 00:24:55.890 align:middle line:84%
neurologically, and you would
emotionally signal your body

00:24:55.890 --> 00:24:59.160 align:middle line:84%
chemically to signal
new genes, to look

00:24:59.160 --> 00:25:01.680 align:middle line:84%
like your brain and body
already had the experience.

00:25:01.680 --> 00:25:03.750 align:middle line:84%
The biological and
neuroscientific model

00:25:03.750 --> 00:25:05.070 align:middle line:90%
says it's possible.

00:25:05.070 --> 00:25:08.610 align:middle line:84%
And if you could get up
as a different person

00:25:08.610 --> 00:25:10.150 align:middle line:90%
than you sat down--

00:25:10.150 --> 00:25:11.910 align:middle line:90%
now here's the key--

00:25:11.910 --> 00:25:14.040 align:middle line:84%
and then to maintain
that modified

00:25:14.040 --> 00:25:16.980 align:middle line:84%
state of being your
entire day, independent

00:25:16.980 --> 00:25:20.370 align:middle line:84%
of your environment,
something unusual

00:25:20.370 --> 00:25:21.990 align:middle line:90%
should happen in your life.

00:25:21.990 --> 00:25:23.250 align:middle line:90%
That's the law.

00:25:23.250 --> 00:25:26.760 align:middle line:84%
So it's like this-- most
people do a meditation.

00:25:26.760 --> 00:25:28.650 align:middle line:90%
They have a great meditation.

00:25:28.650 --> 00:25:31.680 align:middle line:84%
And then they spend the rest of
the day in a state of judgment

00:25:31.680 --> 00:25:34.567 align:middle line:84%
or stress, just like eating
an organic, healthy breakfast

00:25:34.567 --> 00:25:36.900 align:middle line:84%
and then spending the rest
of your day eating junk food.

00:25:36.900 --> 00:25:37.290 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Right.

00:25:37.290 --> 00:25:38.832 align:middle line:84%
>>DISPENZA: The
purpose of meditation

00:25:38.832 --> 00:25:42.240 align:middle line:84%
is to prime the brain and body
into a new state of being,

00:25:42.240 --> 00:25:46.135 align:middle line:84%
to elevate your sense of self
so that the environment is

00:25:46.135 --> 00:25:47.760 align:middle line:84%
no longer-- you're
not effective by it.

00:25:47.760 --> 00:25:50.100 align:middle line:84%
Actually, you've changed
something inside of you,

00:25:50.100 --> 00:25:53.070 align:middle line:84%
both neurologically and
chemically, in mind and body,

00:25:53.070 --> 00:25:55.630 align:middle line:84%
that now you're
beginning to produce

00:25:55.630 --> 00:25:56.880 align:middle line:90%
an effect in your environment.

00:25:56.880 --> 00:26:00.270 align:middle line:84%
So I always recommend,
experiment in your reality.

00:26:00.270 --> 00:26:02.280 align:middle line:90%
We are scientists in our life.

00:26:02.280 --> 00:26:05.490 align:middle line:84%
And if you could say,
OK, I'm taking my time

00:26:05.490 --> 00:26:07.170 align:middle line:90%
out of my busy day today--

