00:32:00.210 --> 00:32:03.090 align:middle line:10%
That's the beauty of
being a human being.

00:32:03.090 --> 00:32:04.900 align:middle line:10%
By the same means,
the person who

00:32:04.900 --> 00:32:08.020 align:middle line:10%
practices suffering and
thinks of all the reasons

00:32:08.020 --> 00:32:10.450 align:middle line:10%
to complain in their
