00:32:13.240 --> 00:32:15.820 align:middle line:10%
for themselves, they're
doing the same exact thing

00:32:15.820 --> 00:32:19.240 align:middle line:10%
neurologically as the person
who's mastering the golf swing

00:32:19.240 --> 00:32:21.980 align:middle line:10%
or mastering different
states of mind.

00:32:21.980 --> 00:32:25.180 align:middle line:10%
The principle is
absolutely the same.

00:32:25.180 --> 00:32:29.020 align:middle line:10%
The effects are different
based on the levels of mind.

00:32:29.020 --> 00:32:31.960 align:middle line:10%
So the repetition
over time not only

00:32:31.960 --> 00:32:34.630 align:middle line:10%
makes the neurons
begin to function

00:32:34.630 --> 00:32:36.400 align:middle line:10%
in more hardwired
patterns, but they

00:32:36.400 --> 00:32:38.470 align:middle line:10%
begin to accommodate
and form more

00:32:38.470 --> 00:32:40.510 align:middle line:10%
stronger connections,
thicker circuits

00:32:40.510 --> 00:32:42.040 align:middle line:10%
to reflect who and where we are.

00:32:42.040 --> 00:32:43.180 align:middle line:10%
We are all masters.

00:32:43.180 --> 00:32:46.030 align:middle line:10%
The question is what have
you memorized so well

00:32:46.030 --> 00:32:48.310 align:middle line:10%
that your internal
order is greater

00:32:48.310 --> 00:32:50.800 align:middle line:10%
than any external
condition in your life.

00:32:50.800 --> 00:32:53.275 align:middle line:10%
>> Even when we become aware
of these destructive emotional

00:32:53.275 --> 00:32:56.980 align:middle line:10%
