00:35:10.210 --> 00:35:11.660 align:middle line:90%
says something different.

00:35:11.660 --> 00:35:14.420 align:middle line:84%
The quantum model
of reality says

00:35:14.420 --> 00:35:17.000 align:middle line:84%
you have to change your
mind and body, thoughts

00:35:17.000 --> 00:35:19.490 align:middle line:84%
