by thought alone.

00:35:39.230 --> 00:35:40.800 align:middle line:84%
To the body, it's
the exact same.

00:35:40.800 --> 00:35:41.600 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: OK.

00:35:41.600 --> 00:35:43.460 align:middle line:84%
>>DISPENZA: So,
