00:36:04.490 --> 00:36:07.130 align:middle line:84%
Because if your brain
and body are beginning

00:36:07.130 --> 00:36:10.520 align:middle line:84%
to respond neurologically
and chemically,

00:36:10.520 --> 00:36:13.040 align:middle line:84%
now you're moving into
a new state of being.

00:36:13.040 --> 00:36:15.140 align:middle line:84%
And if you can get up
